{"tid":441980,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"人夫到殮房跟亡妻道別　竟目睹男護理師正在姦屍","createTime":"2017-10-20T07:42:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-22T09:22:47.000Z","uid":75969,"like":18,"dislike":348,"uniUserReply":93,"replies":[{"pid":"af4006735e5134c199145cc1dea13a8c51a1deb1","tid":441980,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T07:42:15.000Z","msg":"國際中心／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n玻利維亞一名28歲的人妻因病在醫院過世，遺體事後被送往太平間存放，丈夫得知消息後，想要再見妻子最後一面，沒想到到了太平間之後卻發現，愛妻的遺體竟遭到27歲男護理師馬秋查比性侵，讓他憤而衝上去怒毆對方，並隨即報警處理。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2017/10/20/1101568-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2017%2F10%2F20%2F1101568-XXL.jpg&h=e79c5cb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲圖／翻攝自《metro》<br />\n<br />\n根據外媒報導，該名人妻因為肺臟問題在醫院病逝，遺體隨即被送往太平間安置，丈夫想要跟愛妻好好道別，見她最後一面，然而，等到他抵達太平間後，卻目睹男護理師馬秋查比（Grover Macuchapi）正在性侵愛妻的遺體，「我看到他把褲子都脫了，還出現『前前後後』的動作。」<br />\n<br />\n丈夫見狀後立刻衝上去怒毆對方，隨即報警處理。警方調查後指出，這名人妻大約死亡一小時後，遺體就慘遭到馬男護理師侵犯，目前馬秋查比遭控猥褻罪和對遺體不敬等罪。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=306323\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D306323&d=b2Y%2BkDJcXyKZZPO4JsRoT9tKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=790136e6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D306323&h=7f00133d\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=306323</a><br />\n<br />\n屌你老母咁撚變態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7598ab17565bff4c24085bb2d12c15fa5e2a262","tid":441980,"uid":68047,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T07:43:19.000Z","msg":"真係痴撚線公司"},{"pid":"e92099647361ae9dfc5b066228821e8a20a5a9d9","tid":441980,"uid":153618,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T07:43:36.000Z","msg":"仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/f